==毒性==

一般接触和使用矿物油对人类是安全的。[[FDA|FDA]]批准在个人护理产品和化妆品添加矿物油，也可以作为食品添加剂，上限10 mg/kg。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.realself.com/ingredient/mineral-oil |title=Aquaphor Alternatives for Acne-prone Skin? Doctor Answers, Tips |accessdate=2011-07-06 |archive-date=2010-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100114055113/http://www.realself.com/ingredient/mineral-oil |dead-url=no }}</ref>根据2011年3月英国的一个新闻，墨水中使用的矿物油会渗入食物，因为有致癌危险，食品制造商停止使用回收的纸盒作为包装。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/health/healthnews/8367881/Cereal-box-health-warning-after-recycled-cardboard-study.html | location=London | work=The Daily Telegraph | title=Cereal box health warning after recycled cardboard study | date=2011-03-08 | accessdate=2011-07-06 | archive-date=2011-05-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517104135/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/health/healthnews/8367881/Cereal-box-health-warning-after-recycled-cardboard-study.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]将未精制或低度精制的矿物油分類為[[1類致癌物|1類致癌物]]。而高度精制的礦物油則被分類為[[3類致癌物|3類致癌物]]，即不被視作致癌物，但沒有充分證據證明其不具致癌性。<ref>{{cite web |title=Agents Classified by the IARC Monographs |publisher=New York Times |accessdate=31 May 2011 |date= |url=http://graphics8.nytimes.com/packages/flash/health/pdf/ClassificationsGroupOrder-1.pdf |archive-date=2011-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626232831/http://graphics8.nytimes.com/packages/flash/health/pdf/ClassificationsGroupOrder-1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

