==== 化學用途 ====
由於礦物油的化學性質較穩定，因此常用於儲存不穩定的化學品（如[[鹼金屬|鹼金屬]]），以防止其與空氣或水發生反應。<ref name="OU">{{cite web |url=http://www.open.edu/openlearn/science-maths-technology/science/chemistry/alkali-metals |title=Alkali metals |author=The OpenLearn team |work=OpenLearn |publisher=The Open University |accessdate=2012-07-09 |date=2012 |archive-date=2014-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129052111/http://www.open.edu/openlearn/science-maths-technology/science/chemistry/alkali-metals |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

